  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 350°F (176°C).",
    "In a large pot, sauté onions and garlic in olive oil until translucent.",
    "Add carrots and celery; stir well.",
    "Pour in chicken stock cube. Bring to boil then reduce heat.",
    "Simmer for 20 minutes with pepper flakes added last 5 minutes.",
    "Divide stew into bowls and serve hot.",
    "For extra crunch, chill stews slightly before serving.",
    "Ensure poultry is cooked to an internal temperature of 74°C / 165°F (juices run clear, no pink remaining) before serving."
